The CDs-Eu nanoprobe was further evaluated to detect DPA and TC in various actual samples. The recovery rate for DPA detection was 96.77 %–109.90 %, and the relative standard deviation (RSD) is lower than 7.40 % (Table 1
                        ). The results were consistent with those of detecting TC (Table 2
                        ). These results indicated that the CDs-Eu nanoprobe had good accuracy and reliability for detecting DPA and TC in various actual samples.
